{"title":"大道——关于一条路的诞生","authors":["雷抒雁"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":10,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——关于一条路的诞生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷抒雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首先是推土机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以雄辩者的姿态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驳斥那些威严的障碍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整夜、整夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是竭诚的呐喊和宣讲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顽石与颓墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始松动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后一声喘息之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才感慨闹市筑路的艰辛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百倍胜过旷野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掘土机铺开手术台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刀刀划开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地的皮肤……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上水道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下水道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电缆……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须小心翼翼地嫁接"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个未名的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即将诞生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个夏季，都是坑坑洼洼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明和傍晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在落雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一处都蓄满路人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢骚和怨言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走惯旧路的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然感到行路难，心神恍惚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以往对小道的积怨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎突然变得微不足道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推土机很犟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"履带嘎啦啦碾过水坑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥泞当然短暂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很快，人们就看不见那些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裸露着的肌肉与神经"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于光明、关于动力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及血脉一样的水管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然隐没整个夏季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳在大道上滚动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石子冒着火星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恭顺地服从压路机整形"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经远得看不见的“未来”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然逼近，热气腾腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑面而来，伸手可及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道这就是生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多懒于思考的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放慢了脚步在路边学习思索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两排距离很远的路灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在前方交错成一排"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交错到一起的还有绿树和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美人蕉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再远处，仍是我们天天看见的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狭隘和拥挤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崎岖与不平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎瞬间消失"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交通警开始以雪白的手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梳理新的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天傍晚都坐在路边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说是四十年前就看见过这景象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在梦里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：工人出版社）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}